==晚年生涯==
2013年，保羅創立了名為「榮·保羅和平與繁榮研究所」（Ron Paul Institute for Peace and Prosperity）的外交政策[[智庫|智庫]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Ron Paul Is Launching His Own Foreign Policy Institute|url=https://www.businessinsider.com/ron-paul-foreign-policy-institute-2013-4|accessdate=2021-01-13|date=2013-04-13|last=Wyler|first=Grace|publisher=Business Insider|language=en|archive-date=2020-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200108192022/https://www.businessinsider.com/ron-paul-foreign-policy-institute-2013-4|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年他啟動了名為「榮·保羅頻道」（Ron Paul Channel）的網路節目<ref>{{cite news |title=‘The Ron Paul Channel’ Launching This Summer, Wants You To ‘Turn Off Your TV,’ ‘Turn On The Truth’ |url=https://www.huffpost.com/entry/the-ron-paul-channel_n_3569249 |accessdate=2021-01-13 |publisher=HuffPost |date=2013-07-09 |archive-date=2021-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308061357/https://www.huffpost.com/entry/the-ron-paul-channel_n_3569249 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=The Ron Paul Channel: libertarianism 'unfiltered and uninterrupted'|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2013/aug/16/ron-paul-channel-new-show|accessdate=2021-01-13|date=2013-08-16|publisher=the Guardian|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201220045224/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2013/aug/16/ron-paul-channel-new-show|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年5月，保羅宣布終止與「榮·保羅頻道」和「自由之聲」（Voice of Liberty）的關係，並啟動了「榮·保羅自由報告」（Ron Paul Liberty Report）<ref>{{Cite web|title=Ron Paul Ends Relationship with Voices of Liberty|url=http://www.campaignforliberty.org/ron-paul-ends-relationship-voices-liberty-start-new-venture|accessdate=2021-01-13|date=2015-05-07|publisher=Campaign for Liberty|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225094321/http://www.campaignforliberty.org/ron-paul-ends-relationship-voices-liberty-start-new-venture|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2020年9月25日，保羅在直播中出現口齒不清的症狀後，住院治療<ref>{{Cite web|title=Ron Paul hospitalized for 'precautionary' reasons in Texas|url=https://www.foxnews.com/politics/ron-paul-hospitalized-for-precautionary-reasons-in-texas-fox-news-has-learned|accessdate=2021-01-13|date=2020-09-25|last=Ross|first=Lee|work=Fox News|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111065544/https://www.foxnews.com/politics/ron-paul-hospitalized-for-precautionary-reasons-in-texas-fox-news-has-learned|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2021年1月，[[臉書|臉書]]一度以「多次違反社群守則」為由封鎖了保羅的[[粉專|粉專]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Big Brother’s getting hungry? Former congressman Ron Paul locked out of Facebook for undisclosed reasons|url=https://www.rt.com/usa/512197-ron-paul-facebook-lockout/|accessdate=2021-01-13|date=2021-01-11|publisher=RT|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115144001/https://www.rt.com/usa/512197-ron-paul-facebook-lockout/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Facebook censors libertarian Ron Paul|url=https://nypost.com/2021/01/11/facebook-censors-ron-paul/|accessdate=2021-01-13|date=2021-01-11|last=Nelson|first=Steven|work=New York Post|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210401091719/https://nypost.com/2021/01/11/facebook-censors-ron-paul/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

